title: Motorcycle taxi drivers protest low online tariffs
text:
Motorcycle taxi drivers protest low online tariffs 5:41pm BST - 01:26 
Hundreds of Indonesian motorcycle taxi drivers working for start-ups Grab and Go-Jek have called for an end to low online fares and demanded tighter regulation of ride-hailing companies. Silvia Antonioli reports ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
